		<baseDesc>After graduating from the naval academy [PAWN_nameDef] became a commisoned officer in the imperial spacemarine corps.\n\n[PAWN_pronoun] was eventually honored for exceptional service and assigned to the orbital-deployment shock troop division.</baseDesc>
